personal-dashboard-multi-step-dialog-pro:
Current page indicator for the multi-step dialog.

Parameters:
* $1 - Current page
* $2 - Total pages
personal-dashboard-multi-step-dialog-nex: Text for the “Next” button, which navigates to the next page.
personal-dashboard-multi-step-dialog-pre: Text for the “Previous” button, which navigates to the previous page.
personal-dashboard-multi-step-dialog-got: Text for the “Got it” button, which closes the multi-step dialog.
